  "title": "Senior Technician/ Associate Equipment Engineer (Semiconductor) #80372",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/ Semiconductor</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Senior Technician/ Associate Equipment Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tampines</li><li>Working Hours: 12-hours rotating shift</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT + Shift Allowances + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct advanced troubleshooting and carry out repairs on semiconductor production equipment.</li><li>Design and execute both preventive and corrective maintenance programs to reduce machine downtime.</li><li>Oversee maintenance initiatives and collaborate with various departments to ensure seamless implementation.</li><li>Assess and propose new tools and technologies to improve operational efficiency and process performance.</li><li>Guide and support junior team members in building their technical skills.</li><li>Contribute to the formulation, evaluation, and enhancement of maintenance protocols and best practices.</li><li>Work closely with external equipment providers to troubleshoot issues and strengthen system reliability.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Higher NITEC in Electrical, Electronic, Mechanical Engineering, or a related discipline.</li><li>At least 3 years of technical experience in Semiconductor industry</li><li>Demonstrated ability to troubleshoot and fix complex equipment issues.</li><li>Comfortable working in a cleanroom environment on a 12-hour rotating schedule.</li><li>Willing to commit to overtime when necessary to meet production demands.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80372 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
